# =============================================================================
# Imperishable Gate Client Configuration File
# Imperishable Gate 客户端配置文件
# =============================================================================
# Copy this file to .env and modify with actual configuration values
# Place this file in the client executable directory or project root directory
# 复制此文件为 .env 并修改为实际配置值
# 将此文件放在客户端可执行文件所在目录或项目根目录

# =============================================================================
# Server Configuration
# 服务器配置
# =============================================================================
# Gate server address
# Important: Must include protocol prefix (http:// or https://), otherwise defaults to https://
# Gate 服务器地址
# 重要：必须包含协议前缀（http:// 或 https://），否则默认使用 https://
# 
# Development environment example:
# 开发环境示例：
GATE_SERVER_ADDR=http://localhost:4514

# Production environment example:
# 生产环境示例：
# GATE_SERVER_ADDR=https://gate.example.com

# Custom port:
# 自定义端口：
# GATE_SERVER_ADDR=http://192.168.1.100:8080

# =============================================================================
# Notes
# 注意事项
# =============================================================================
# 1. Protocol prefix is required!
#    Correct: http://localhost:4514
#    Wrong: localhost:4514 (will be parsed as https://localhost:4514)
#    1. 协议前缀是必需的！
#       正确: http://localhost:4514
#       错误: localhost:4514（会被解析为 https://localhost:4514）
#
# 2. Can also be set via environment variable:
#    export GATE_SERVER_ADDR=http://localhost:4514
#    2. 也可以通过环境变量设置：
#       export GATE_SERVER_ADDR=http://localhost:4514
#
# 3. Can also be set via command line argument:
#    ./gate --addr http://localhost:4514 <command>
#    3. 也可以通过命令行参数设置：
#       ./gate --addr http://localhost:4514 <command>
#
# 4. Priority: Command line argument > GATE_SERVER_ADDR > SERVER_ADDR > Default value
#    4. 优先级：命令行参数 > GATE_SERVER_ADDR > SERVER_ADDR > 默认值
